<DOCNO> LA051194-0053 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 040467 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
May 11, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 1; Column 5; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
