</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 "Sarajevo Ground Zero," a controversial documentary capturing the brutality of 
civil war in Sarajevo, debuts on cable's Cinemax tonight at 8. 
</P>
<P>
 Produced by a multiethnic group of Bosnian filmmakers, the movie was turned 
down for broadcast by the various networks. 
</P>
