Arlington at Central Union, Claremont at Apple Valley, Temecula Valley at 
Riverside J.W. North, Calexico at Palm Springs, Glendale at North Torrance, Los 
Amigos at Laguna Beach, Esperanza at La Quinta, Encino Crespi at Montebello 
Schurr. 
</P>
<P>
 Division III -- Burbank Burroughs at Santa Maria, Whittier La Serna at 
Cerritos Whitney, Pacific at Alta Loma, Rosemead at Palos Verdes Chadwick, 
Ontario Chaffey at Mira Loma Jurupa Valley, Western at Walnut. 
</P>
<P>
 First round 
</P>
<P>
