Long Beach Poly at La Puente Nogales, West Covina at San Marino, South Pasadena 
at Beverly Hills, San Clemente at Ocean View, Villa Park at Mission Viejo, 
Lakewood at Corona del Mar, Anaheim Canyon at Dana Hills, Woodbridge at Edison, 
