</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 KROQ will be throwing its second annual "Weenie Roast and Sing-a-Long at the 
Irvine Meadows Amphitheatre, 8800 Irvine Center Drive, on June 11. 
</P>
