 Nuclear weapons -- Headings in a chart published Tuesday comparing the U.S. 
and former Soviet nuclear arsenals were reversed.This is how the chart should 
have read. 05,12,11,10,11,10 *2*UNITED STATES *2*FORMER SOVIETS Based in: 
Launchers Warheads Launchers Warheads Silos 730 2,240 1,067 5,905 Submarines 
336 2,688 520 2,384 Bombers 192 3,452 109 1,374 TOTAL 1,258 8,380 1,696 9,663  
